{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20191.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime04","chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-1"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, she hasn't turned up yet?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-2"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That's right."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-3"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I tried to ask her parents..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-4"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But it seems like she hasn't@contacted them at all since leaving."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm sure she won't have any issues@with funds, at least..."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-6"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But I really didn't expect her@to suddenly disappear."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-7"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Thanks to your magic, the painful@memories were cleanly cut out..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But that doesn't mean her family's issues@were resolved."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If anything, maybe she lost an outlet@for her frustrations..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-10"},{"eyeClose":0,"id":200501}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But it's not something you need@to worry about, Mami."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-11"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I mean, not only did she pull a no-show..."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...She also made you deal with the Witch@that appeared there all on your own."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200906,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I think that's pretty rude of her."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-14"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Mami?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]No, it's nothing."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Nothing...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]No way. There IS something wrong,@isn't there?"},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What is it?@What are you so worried about?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-20"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-21"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mami!"},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Aren't we...friends?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......[wait:1.2][chara:200501:lipSynch_1][chara:200501:voiceFull_fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-23]Mabayu."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-24","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-23"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I didn't...have a fight with her@after that, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]A fight?"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-26"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm sorry, Mabayu."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I know that I shouldn't be suspecting@something like this..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-28"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But...it still crosses my mind."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-29"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]What if she and I had a falling out,@and ended up fighting...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-30"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]And what if you erased my memory@of that...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200906,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-31"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-32"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mami, please listen carefully."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-33"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I swear it on our friendship."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-34"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I would never take away your memories."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-35"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mabayu..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-36"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Remember, I can see the future."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-37"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If my actions made you anxious,@that would kind of defeat the@point of cutting out memories."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-38"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If I really WERE to take your memories..."},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":400,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-39"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'd do it so perfectly,@you wouldn't even suspect it's gone!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200906}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200501,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-40","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-39"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes...@That does seem more your style."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913008-001-40"}]},"version":3}
